# text = pañcāśadvarṣāṇi kāyavāṅmanovihāravaiṣamyam śarādiprahāraḥ cittodvegaḥ dehadhāraṇadhātuśabde dravabhāvaḥ gacchanneva itthaṃbhūtena kriyāphalasiddhiṃ abhidadhāmīti ityādikam ātmaprakṛtivikārasaṃmūrchitaṃ dṛṣṭārtavaḥ ātmādayo pañcāśadvarṣāṇi śarādiprahāraḥ kāyavāṅmanovihāravaiṣamyam dehadhāraṇadhātuśabde kriyāphalasiddhiṃ ātmaprakṛtivikārasaṃmūrchitaṃ kāyavāṅmanovihāravaiṣamyam dehadhāraṇadhātuśabde ātmaprakṛtivikārasaṃmūrchitaṃ kāyavāṅmanovihāravaiṣamyam prādhānyāttataḥ ca vyāpnoti sa indriyārthavaiṣamyaṃ bhayaṃ rāgamupaitītyanenaiva ayam ṛtukālajaṃ nocyante pratibaddhā tena tejasā tiṣṭhati ityucyata 'visrāvya loke saumyājjātam naro pratyekaṃ vṛddhānām yathā bhavanti saṃbandhaḥ
